name: Series of studies, 01
description: I like to imagine that all screens, canvas or pixels are a place where I can go inside. So I make self portraits as any artists does. It has beeing a great discover to paint in the digital canvas. This one was my second study wich I liked a lot. This work open the study series where I am gonna share works that don't belong to any other collection. I hope I can bring good energies to your screen!
